|c|☆godiamsosorry|Tbh Enam feels like Azelf a bit but I am unsure.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|In the Azelf sus Azelf swept A LOT.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|Especially compared to now where generally it is a little too frail to do serious damage.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|Ithink people are just not prepared for Enam.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|But, I also do think Enam is a bit more volatile than Azelf.
|c|☆Dragon Master Rosa|true

|c|☆godiamsosorry|Like it is just way harder to revenge kill, especially since it resists stuff like Sucker and isn´t weak to things like Zoro Shadow Sneak or faster U-turns.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|It also becomes virtually unkillable on one attacking spectrum.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|And there aren´t many faster special attackers, barring Azelf, which can outspeed and threaten it.
|c|☆Dragon Master Rosa|yeah
|c|☆godiamsosorry|Especially with Sub, it probably is wraps if it can get to +2.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|As of now I am leaning toward voting ban.
|c|☆Dragon Master Rosa|fair
|c|☆godiamsosorry|That is not, however, to say that this has not been valuable information.
|c|☆godiamsosorry|No matter the result, this suspect will be good for collecting data.
